metadata.description:
TwelveFold by Yuga Labs is an experimental limited edition collection of 300 generative artworks inscribed on satoshis on the Bitcoin blockchain.
These pieces represent a complete art project and will not have any other use, interact with, or be linked to any previous, ongoing, or future Ethereum-based Yuga project.
The NFTs you have purchased will be eligible for transfer on the Bitcoin blockchain.
For more information on the inspiration for why
Yuga Labs decided to create TwelveFold.
metadata.name: Twelvefold Ordinals #1
